structure.unit: COUNTY AND CITY BRIDGES, TUNNELS, AND FERRIES

law.history: Repealed 1984 Ky. Acts ch. 113, sec. 8, effective July 13, 1984. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 3235g-24.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Competing bridges and ferries must have permit.
